# Sam YT Shorts Engine — secrets
#
# Copy this file to ".env" (same folder) and paste in YOUR OWN ElevenLabs key.
# The engine uses ElevenLabs for two things: Scribe transcription + per-clip music.
# Both bill to whatever key is in here — so this MUST be your own key, not anyone else's.
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#   then edit .env and replace the placeholder below.
#
# .env is gitignored, so your key is never committed or shared.
# Get a key at: https://elevenlabs.io  (Profile -> API Keys)

ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your_elevenlabs_key_here
